Package: circlesplot
Type: Package
Title: Visualize Proportions with Circles in a Plot
Version: 0.1.0
Author: BenSt099
Maintainer: BenSt099 <benst099@proton.me>
Description: This library provides tools to plot multiple circles with their given diameter.
    The circles are used to visualize proportions between different objects, e.g. planets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Imports:
    plotrix
